          <title>Airlines adopt software fix for Airbus A320 after plane has sudden altitude drop</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Airlines around the world canceled and delayed flights heading into the weekend to fix software on a widely used commercial plane after an analysis found computer code may have contributed to a sudden drop in the altitude of a JetBlue aircraft last month.]]></description>
